  <description>
    <p>A great music app.</p>
    <p>Features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>User-friendly interface: Musily has an intuitive and easy-to-use interface.</li>
      <li>Powerful search: Easily find songs, artists, and albums using our advanced search bar.</li>
      <li>Offline playback: Download your favorite songs and listen to them without an internet connection.</li>
      <li>Comets!</li>
      <li>Dinosaurs!</li>
      <li>Library management: Create and edit custom playlists.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
